Subject: Buses By the Beach - Live Music Line Up

Hello Fellow Bus Pilots,

We are so excited that we are only a few weeks away from the 8th Annual Bus
Benefit hosted by Buses By the Beach in Grand Rapids, MI May 20-23! (Always
held the weekend before Memorial Day Weekend) This event is held to raise
money for the Phoenix Society for Burn Survivors.
http://www.phoenix-society.org/
<http://app.expressemailmarketing.com/get.link?linkid=2077886&subscriberid=5
4974315&campaignid=553403&linkurl=http%3a%2f%2fwww.phoenix-society.org%2f> 

This year is shaping up to be a spectacular year with some spectacular live
music. Below is a list of some of the artists that will be performing at
this year's event. 

*	Live music from several artists playing their blend of roots rock,
folk, bluegrass, jam and singer song writer genres. As in years past we
showcases some fine home grown Michigan music. There is a lot of great music
coming out of our state in recent years and it is nice to have an
opportunity to share their music with others from other parts of the
country. Performing this year will be:

*	Jen Sygit - http://www.jensygit.com/
<http://app.expressemailmarketing.com/get.link?linkid=2077889&subscriberid=5
4974315&campaignid=553403&linkurl=http%3a%2f%2fwww.jensygit.com%2f>  
*	Sam Corbin - http://www.samcorbin.com/
<http://app.expressemailmarketing.com/get.link?linkid=2077890&subscriberid=5
4974315&campaignid=553403&linkurl=http%3a%2f%2fwww.samcorbin.com%2f>  
