We are looking forward to seeing old friends again and getting a chance to
meet new ones. If you would like to attend Bus Benefit and need more
information please feel free to go to our website and either read up on the
forum or join the email news list. www.busesbythebeach.com
<http://www.busesbythebeach.com/> 

Wishing you many miles of smiles!

